{"tid":2267882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國半官方證實：美國務卿專機飛越半個中國領空","createTime":"2020-11-02T11:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T11:47:53.000Z","uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5713604a07fcdaafd1330c9684a382999c438619","tid":2267882,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:29:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美軍機飛越中國領空 機上「大人物」身分曝光</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n2020/11/02 00:46<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/01/php6hfaiY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2Fphp6hfaiY.jpg&h=51fbf990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國半官方美軍動態追蹤機構指出，1架美國空軍飛機飛入中國領土，從上海出海。（圖取自SCSPI）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）10月26日展開南亞行，先後訪問印度、斯里蘭卡、馬爾地夫、印尼，並臨時追加29日、30日訪問越南；<span class=\"red\">追蹤美軍動態的中國半官方機構指稱，龐皮歐搭乘的美國空軍專機從越南飛越中國領空，直達日本。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/01/phpqjGluj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2FphpqjGluj.jpg&h=8e64cea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龐皮歐30日結束越南訪問行程，搭機離開。（圖取自龐皮歐推特）<br />\n<br />\n依美國國務院官網新聞稿，龐皮歐10月29日至30日前往越南河內，會見越南總統阮富仲及副總理兼外交部長范平明，龐皮歐此行是慶祝美、越建交25周年，重申全面合作，並討論雙方都很關心的南海、湄公河地區等議題，美國尊重越南的權利和利益，並以符合國際法的方式維護和平與海洋自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/01/phpz83cv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F01%2Fphpz83cv1.jpg&h=37dc1c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越南官員向龐皮歐等人揮手致意。（圖取自龐皮歐推特）<br />\n<br />\n龐皮歐在推特指出，在河內舉行了一些重要會議，很高興再次見到越南朋友，並重申美國對越南的承諾，龐皮歐也貼出他登機離開的照片，他向停機坪的越南官員們揮手致意，越南官員們也回禮；但美國國務院並未透露龐皮歐的後續行程。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中國半官方性質丶北京大學「南海戰略態勢感知計畫」（SCSPI）30日晚間在推特宣稱，龐皮歐離開越南河內時，搭乘美國空軍C-32A專機穿越中國領空，從廣西飛入後，沿途經過廣東、江西、浙江上空，最後從上海附近出海直飛日本</span>；該機構意有所指地說「很高興在激烈的美中競爭中，還能見到（雙方）這樣的互動」。不過，美方並未對此加以證實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SCS_PI/status/1322124345767055360?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCS_PI%2Fstatus%2F1322124345767055360%3Fs%3D20&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=27aea162\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSCS_PI%2Fstatus%2F1322124345767055360%3Fs%3D20&h=d8fc15a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SCS_PI/status/1322124345767055360?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3338885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3338885&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxcls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=cfa1486b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3338885&h=864f126d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3338885</a>"},{"pid":"e581e8b83439adf16fe3e486de09b924677af79f","tid":2267882,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:31:08.000Z","msg":"FRIEND返囉而家咩事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330a2864a8fb58e055d69d16451ad5f89b6a2e59","tid":2267882,"uid":331421,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:31:12.000Z","msg":"美軍來了我帶.....美軍走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a281b1fb2dc3e396c6d8052989377bbc5b2dcbfd","tid":2267882,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"龐皮歐離開越南河內時，搭乘美國空軍C-32A專機穿越中國領空，從廣西飛入後，沿途經過廣東、江西、浙江上空，最後從上海附近出海直飛日本"},{"pid":"d9719044229e82fc84a44a0617f6fa565b3c4973","tid":2267882,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"美國：門戶開放政策2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im